s, and the Wright Brothers, the book encourages leaders to inspire loyalty and drive success with a clear sense of purpose.','2009-10-28 00:00:00.000','Finance & Business','https://imgs.search.brave.com/SWDjFMULE5IUn6Vmuh2u5j-UUWIdvZ-y2jLhPkWOh-0/rs:fit:500:0:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu/cGVuZ3Vpbi5jby51/ay9fbmV4dC9pbWFn/ZT91cmw9aHR0cHM6/Ly9jZG4ucGVuZ3Vp/bi5jby51ay9kYW0t/YXNzZXRzL2Jvb2tz/Lzk3ODE0MDU5Nzc1/OTMvOTc4MTQwNTk3/NzU5My1qYWNrZXQt/bGFyZ2UuanBnJnc9/ODE5JnE9MTAw','2025-10-24 13:46:52.649',NULL,1,'English',271,'https://www.earthgifts.com.au/ebook/simon-sinek-start-with-why.pdf','2025-11-18 19:10:45.781','https://res.cloudinary.com/dajcb1ir2/raw/upload/v1763493045/NovelVerse/books/start-with-why:-how-great-leaders-inspire-everyone-to-take-action/tqlx70g4juszs7qgmfo9.json',1,'start-with-why:-how-great-leaders-inspire-everyone-to-take-action'),('3a7e8b2f-5623-4c85-a6d0-2f3b1379396f','Sapiens: A Brief History of Humankind','Yuval Noah Harari','Sapiens explores the history of the human species from the emergence of Homo sapiens in the Stone Age through the Cognitive, Agricultural, and Scientific Revolutions, up to the modern era. Harari examines how shared beliefs and imagined realities—such as religion, money, and politics—have shaped human culture and enabled large-scale cooperation. The book questions progress, human wellbeing, and our species’ impact on the planet, encouraging readers to reflect on our past and future trajectory.','2011-01-01 00:00:00.000','Science & Technology','https://imgs.search.brave.com/2IXAbk7dHSWSpRYhfua8iRM-hqfKGRvh3v_bBICUJ9Y/rs:fit:500:0:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu/dG9zdW1tYXJpc2Uu/Y29tL3dwLWNvbnRl/bnQvdXBsb2Fkcy8y/MDIyLzA2L0hhcmFy/aS1TYXBpZW5zLmpw/Zw','2025-10-24 14:07:42.175',NULL,0,'English',480,'https://dn720005.ca.archive.org/0/items/sapiens_202112/Sapiens.pdf','2025-11-18 19:26:45.967','https://res.cloudinary.com/dajcb1ir2/raw/upload/v1763494005/NovelVerse/books/sapiens:-a-brief-history-of-humankind/dg5swg8zm3jteliklpm0.json',1,'sapiens:-a-brief-history-of-humankind'),('40fd6ffa-ec05-4bc4-80f8-fe215fee29b4','Atomic Habits','James Clear','A practical guide to breaking bad habits and developing good ones using tiny, incremental changes. Focuses on small adjustments, habit loops, and designing environments for lasting change.','2018-10-16 00:00:00.000','Self-Help & Personal Development','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/06/Atomic_habits.jpg','2025-10-24 06:40:02.402',NULL,1,'English',285,'https://dn710008.ca.archive.org/0/items/atomic-habits-by-james-clear.pdf/Atomic%20Habits%20by%20James%20Clear.pdf.pdf','2025-11-18 19:36:51.672','https://res.cloudinary.com/dajcb1ir2/raw/upload/v1763494611/NovelVerse/books/atomic-habits/nbb4gnmq0nwhjsdq9dz2.json',1,'atomic-habits'),('41044243-02d3-408b-bb00-249a3dbf1e2d','Astrophysics for People in a Hurry','Neil deGrasse Tyson','Astrophysics for People in a Hurry offers an accessible introduction to the universe’s biggest mysteries, from the Big Bang and black holes to dark matter, dark energy, and quantum mechanics. Neil deGrasse Tyson distills complex topics into concise, engaging explanations written for readers with limited time. The book captures the wonder of the cosmos while providing a clear understanding of how humanity fits into the universal story. It combines scientific insight with Tyson’s signature wit and clarity, making astrophysics approachable for everyone.','2017-05-02 00:00:00.000','Science & Technology','https://imgs.search.brave.com/nyfpnc2qSoattO0Fyw4Eq3czPXWV8i787kZg1i08z7c/rs:fit:500:0:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmVi/YXlpbWcuY29tL2lt/YWdlcy9nL1Y0MEFB/T1N3dXhGWXRCbGwv/cy1sMjI1LmpwZw','2025-10-24 14:22:17.108',NULL,0,'English',109,'https://dn790001.ca.archive.org/0/items/astrophysicsforpeopleinahurrybyneildegrassetysonpdfdrive.com/Astrophysics%20For%20People%20In%20A%20Hurry%20by%20Neil%20deGrasse%20Tyson%20%28%20PDFDrive.com%20%29.pdf','2025-11-18 19:40:27.332','https://res.cloudinary.com/dajcb1ir2/raw/upload/v1763494826/NovelVerse/books/astrophysics-for-people-in-a-hurry/weerdnwfit1j3hcamrnj.json',1,'astrophysics-for-people-in-a-hurry'),('4314c9c2-4579-4121-89ff-dee3fe2951d9','Game of Thrones The Ice and Fire','George R.R. Martin','A Song of Ice and Fire is a sweeping epic fantasy series set in the fictional continents of Westeros and Essos. The story chronicles the brutal and complex political and dynastic struggles among noble families vying for control of the Iron Throne and dominion over the Seven Kingdoms. The saga features deeply complex characters, intertwining plots of betrayal, alliance, war, and magic, alongside the looming threat of the supernatural Others from the far North. The series explores themes of power, loyalty, honor, and the blurred lines between good and evil, offering a realistic and dark take on traditional fantasy tropes.','1996-08-06 00:00:00.000','Fantasy & Adventure','https://imgs.search.brave.com/zD2_b0fNMArUBywbvhdQyrTatcHIs_PbY-Rr_pEURCg/rs:fit:500:0:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9lY3Nt/ZWRpYS5wbC9jZG4t/Y2dpL2ltYWdlL3dp/ZHRoPTU0NCxoZWln/aHQ9NTQ0LC9jL2Et/c29uZy1vZi1pY2Ut/YW5kLWZpcmUtMDEt/YS1nYW1lLW9mLXRo/cm9uZXMtYi1pZXh0/NDQxNjkxMzcuanBn','2025-10-24 17:24:26.184',NULL,1,'English',755,'https://www.nothuman.net/images/files/discussion/1/e72f9f1f181a66887baa7270037c582e.pdf','2025-11-19 04:08:45.249','https://res.cloudinary.com/dajcb1ir2/raw/upload/v1763525325/NovelVerse/books/game-of-thrones-the-ice-and-fire/ji1zqamtkko0aojj1wju.json',1,'game-of-thrones-the-ice-and-fire'),('437a3160-03b4-4e22-8c4e-17abb7339a9e','The Hobbit, or There and Back Again','J.R.R. Tolkien','The Hobbit is a beloved fantasy novel that follows the journey of Bilbo Baggins, a quiet and comfort-loving hobbit, who is thrust into an epic adventure when the wizard Gandalf and a group of dwarves recruit him to reclaim their stolen treasure from the dragon Smaug. Along the way, Bilbo encounters trolls, goblins, giant spiders, elves, and Gollum, from whom he acquires the mysterious One Ring. What begins as